                     <interp inst="t18280911-180-person1039" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I received this piece of ribbon from the witness - it has the private-mark on it; I asked the prisoner how she came to take it - she said she did not take it; I began to search her, and found this other piece of ribbon in her bosom, which has no mark on it; she would not say where she lived.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 28.</p>
